data.description: Welcome to this fabulous 5 bedroom home in Homestead Heights built in 2018. Enjoy the cozy study/office room with french doors as you walk in. The bright living room area features a gas fireplace and the beautiful gourmet kitchen features double ovens, gas cook-top, two under mount sinks, granite countertops and much more. You will love the big backyard with an extended deck to enjoy memories with your family and friends! Not only that, you will also have room to add a shed and anything else you may desire. Upper level features 4 bedrooms including laundry room and 2 full bathrooms. Basement is fully finished and includes a family room, bedroom and full bathroom. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your home, schedule your showing today!
